sentences: Sanela Sijerčić is a Bosnian folk singer from Sarajevo.
She has released six albums and received a "Folk Oscar" in 2006.
She has also been named the "Female singer of the year" (in Bosnia).
She reportedly "retired" from active recording and performing by 2009.
